_header: Here commences a book of swevening / That men metteth in sleeping
_description: The Interpretation of Dreams — in couplets

BLHar2253.First Lines:
Her commensez a bok of sweuenyng þat men metteþ in
                    slepyng…
BLHar2253.Last Lines:
…he vs wyte & warde bo ant euer shilde vs from vr
                    fo
